Params: {2: 'Lee', 3: "I'm alright. I was just a little careless.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I thought I told you not to come.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'How could we stay behind with everything going on out here?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "We've always been the scapegoats. Everyone's just used to it.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "However we are rejected, we've accepted it as our fate no matter how resentful we may be.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "You're the only one to never back down... Maybe this is why everyone looks up to you so much, Rosetta.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "It's been an honor to have you as my mentor.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "I just didn't expect this day to come so soon...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Why would you... want to... fight for those humans...?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Forest Guards, spread out! Protect New Murmansk!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I'll be okay. Someone of your capability is better off helping them in battle.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Go save the others. I'll take care of Rosetta.", 4: '2'}
